- [x] **Evaluation Schemas**: Defined Pydantic schema constraints under [schemas/](file:///d:/2026/college%20pro/hack/api/llm/schemas) for:
  - JD Audit (`jd_audit_schema.py`)
  - Ghost Candidate (`ghost_candidate_schema.py`)
