  - Behaviour (`behaviour_schema.py`)
  - Credibility (`credibility_schema.py`)
  - Insider Signals (`insider_signal_schema.py`)
  - Ghost Comparison (`ghost_comparison_schema.py`)
  - Interrogation (`interrogation_schema.py`)
- [x] **Evaluation Prompts**: Defined system and user prompt blueprints under [prompts/](file:///d:/2026/college%20pro/hack/api/llm/prompts) for each component.

---

## 5. Advanced AI Reasoning Engine

- [x] **Semantic Router**: Classifies incoming query strings to resolve target specialist agents.
- [x] **Self-Reflection (Reflector)**: Logic to critique drafts and run correction passes for logical errors.
- [x] **Tree of Thought (ToT) Explorer**: Generates three parallel evaluation pathways and scores/picks the best candidate path.
- [x] **Mixture of Agents (MoA) Orchestrator**: Executes Trajectory, Behaviour, Credibility, and Insider Signal analyzers in parallel and merges them using the Ghost Comparator.
- [x] **Prompt Engine Interface**: Unified [PromptEngine](file:///d:/2026/college%20pro/hack/api/llm/engine.py#L297) class exposed for clean execution.

---

## 6. Pending Pipelines & Business Logic

- [x] **Resume Ingestion Pipeline**: Document text extraction parsing for `.pdf` and `.docx` with scanned image fallback OCR (`pypdfium2` and `pytesseract`).
- [x] **BYOK Key Management**: AES-256-GCM encryption/decryption utilities using cryptography and HKDF org key derivation.
- [x] **Celery Tasks Execution**: Asynchronous parsing, evaluations, and cohort reporting tasks fully integrated into worker queue routing.
- [x] **Score Fusion & Ranking Engine**: Core scoring mathematics applying slider weights/presets, flag penalties, and diversity-reshuffling pass.
- [x] **Pool Health Aggregator**: Statistics compilation, qualifications estimation, over/under-claimed skill checklists, hidden gems, and LLM pool narrative builder.

---

## 7. API Routing & Security Middleware

- [x] **Auth Middleware**: Implement JWT authentication and role checking middleware using Supabase token verification in [auth.py](file:///d:/2026/college%20pro/hack/api/utils/auth.py) and integrated into [index.py](file:///d:/2026/college%20pro/hack/api/index.py).
- [ ] **REST Endpoints**:
  - `POST /api/v1/projects` (Create project, select BYOK key, audit JD, generate Ghost candidate).
  - `POST /api/v1/projects/{id}/resumes` (Batch resume upload endpoint triggering Celery queue tasks).
  - `GET /api/v1/projects/{id}/candidates` (Fetch ranked candidates with real-time scoring data).
  - `GET /api/v1/projects/{id}/dashboard` (Retrieve Pool Health cohort metrics).
  - `GET /api/v1/projects/{id}/export` (Generate ranked candidate CSV).
- [ ] **Global Error Handler**: Add FastAPI exception handlers mapping HTTP exceptions globally and hiding internal stack traces in production.
- [ ] **Security Auditing & Logging**: Masks sensitive parameters (like API keys) in trace logs and populates `audit_logs` database entries on user actions.
